object.customQuery:
with current_batch as (
select
	bls.batch_id,
	bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
	bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
from
	$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
where
	bls.source_system_code ='$$sourcesystemcode'
	and bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
	and bls.batch_id = (
	select
		MAX(batch_id)
	from
		$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
	where
		source_system_code ='$$sourcesystemcode'
		and batch_status = 'Inprogress' ) )
SELECT 
    DISTINCT 
    acp.source_name, 
    acp.load_type, 
    acp.agency_nup, 
    acp.bs_appoint_dt, 
    acp.bs_cancel_dt, 
    acp.ca_appoint_dt, 
    acp.ca_cancel_dt, 
    acp.create_user_nup, 
    acp.created, 
    acp.id, 
    acp.mk_appoint_dt, 
    acp.mk_cancel_dt, 
    acp.modified, 
    acp.modify_user_nup, 
    acp.state,
    cb.batch_id
FROM 
    $$raw_schema.adm_commission_plans acp
CROSS JOIN current_batch cb
ORDER BY 
    acp.id,
    acp.created,
    acp.modified;

object.customQuery:
SELECT 
	adm_commission_plans_row_id, 
	agency_nup,
	id,
        adm_commission_plans_md5checksum
FROM $$staging_schema.adm_commission_plans
WHERE adm_commission_plans_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
